# Description
# This file is the PPP file for the following modem:
#               Skywire LTE CAT1 bis Global Modem: NL-SW-LTE-QC1bisWWG
#               This file is specifically for using the NL-SW-LTE-QC1bisWWG on Verizon
#
# Instructions
#       1.      You will need to add your APN in the file: vzw-QC1bisWWG-chat
#       2.      This file is setup for PPP over UART. If you use USB, it may enumerate differently in /dev/.
#               Change the line:
#                       /dev/ttyUSB0
#               to however the Skywire enumerates for you.
#

/dev/ttyUSB0
115200
connect "/usr/sbin/chat -v -f /etc/ppp/peers/vzw-QC1bisWWG-chat"
noauth
crtscts
defaultroute
usepeerdns
local
debug
updetach
refuse-pap
+ipv6
